{
  "stem": "21482.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I wouldn't have had a chance to get married and have children and grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Like my cousins that were, you know, just as smart as me and just as cute me-- more, but were not given a chance-- were not given a chance to survive.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Brunnlitz?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By midnight, he had to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The war was over, and he would be a war criminal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he change-- he and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Schindler changed in prisoners' uniforms, even though they didn't look like prisoners because they had hair.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he opened the warehouses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had a warehouse where he had a lot of textiles, and gave orders to the-- he-- to the young boys, our young Jewish men.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had made contact with the Czech underground, and they-- they armed our boys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was-- Oskar Schindler was going to leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He gave orders that every one of us was going to get, like, three yards of fabric and a bottle of whiskey and a pair of slippers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was going to be our money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's what was in the warehouse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the boys were going to guard us with the guns, because the German army was retreating and there was still danger somebody would come in and kill us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we gave him the ring.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They made a ring for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Out of gold that was in somebody's tooth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a few men that still had gold teeth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See, if they went through Auschwitz, they would not have had gold teeth, but the men went to Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- some of them still had the teeth, so they took the gold out and made the ring.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The men went to Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
